>\n<br />\n唔通每段婚姻嘅結束都係背叛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有理性分析caca傻，但唔係有第三者就話人臭雞。<br />\n<br />\n成十年情呀，我唔信無啦啦見到個𡃁仔就飛甩咳神，佢地之間嘅事你地又知幾多呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"1.點解藝人唔可以做例子？<br />\n2.咁佢哋之間嘅事你又知幾多？十年情？係一齊喺十年啫，你又知CACA有投放感情入去？你嘛一樣靠估。"},{"pid":"74aeffa1f13ef7597baed0de93757e3b7e506c05","tid":545911,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"無聊，本性係雞格改都改唔到架啦，天生淫蕩做唔到個賢妻就做唔到啦"},{"pid":"53cd4bfaacbc289a0a07382aff1f20cb259ea012","tid":545911,"uid":23707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"係錯, 但係有原因<br />\n<br />\n咁算唔算錯?<br />\n<br />\n錯就認啦屌你老味 係度兜"},{"pid":"cfab369940ee89d82d390c0fdd6df89e00b4c138","tid":545911,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"我諗真係要等咳神出黎，你地等炒車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個女人要玩外遇根本唔洗咁高調，大可以一邊住咳神，一邊偷偷地同條uber仔搞野。會唔會ig post晒相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n偷食仲會post ig？你地班連登仔會唔會太思維簡單？你估caca會唔會豬成咁？<br />\n<br />\n一邊留住咳神，一邊玩小鮮肉唔好？呢啲先叫臭雞囉！"},{"pid":"8cadb4e55d4c4fba7ddd46b6d8d1e2382b556b29","tid":545911,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f434bdb52552e2c75dad76abc8b450fc690bd22b","tid":545911,"uid":73492,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"Caca同樓主一樣 都係臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"師兄識波"},{"pid":"1f2c5bc1b7084881c7a8f41a7438ffb3faaab4bf","tid":545911,"uid":23707,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cfab369940ee89d82d390c0fdd6df89e00b4c138","tid":545911,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25